  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Founded in 2018, Faalcon Concepts Limited deals with the planning, design, fabrication, and installation of façade systems.</p>\n<p>The company offers facades resistant to UV rays, acid rain, dust, noise, and other influences. Faalcon Concepts' product portfolio includes glazing/curtain walls, aluminium doors and windows, skylights, canopies, frameless glazing, MS structures, stone cladding, metal cladding, and roofing.</p>\n<p>The company's customer list includes companies like Espirit Techno Consultant Pvt. Ltd, Galaxy Magnum Infra Height Limited, Babbar Films, Maconns Infra Pvt. Ltd, Silvers 107 Stone Regency Pvt. Ltd, St Xavier School, Gurgaon High School etc. The company has catered to customers in various states like Haryana, Uttar Pradesh, Rajasthan, Madhya Pradesh, Karnataka, Gujrat, Punjab, Delhi and overseas.</p>\n<p>As of December 23, 2023, the company had 26 employees.</p>"
  },
